{"tid":1846327,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"請問每間醫院最近既警察局係邊？費時一陣又走犯又打人","createTime":"2020-01-27T14:40:06.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-27T14:46:02.000Z","uid":263448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"6c5d8c1b23a887f3cda38a96220792d8f63be5c1","tid":1846327,"uid":263448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T14:40:06.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">新聞有講，有病人逃走</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">傳聞就話有病人打醫護、扯口罩、吐口水、甚至殺死篤灰既人。</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n醫護既武力近乎0，係理大一役已經睇得出佢地好輕易咁比忠誠勇毅既香港警察捉住。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n依家不得不求下忠誠勇毅既香港警察，希望佢地可以係39分鐘以內趕到現場制服逃亡既病人。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">所以請問每間醫院最近既警察局係邊？</span></strong></span><br />\n咁我地可以即時到警局求助啊嘛~<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/or4aHPn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2For4aHPn.jpg&h=e974b6e0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/i0ZFkA2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fi0ZFkA2.png&h=c266fc82&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n屯門醫院既香港警察神龍見首不見尾，應該係用專業既眼光捉緊啲想潛逃既病人，不過雙拳單槍難敵百病人，<span style=\"color: red;\">建議駐院警察增加至百人，費時唔夠人手啦！</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1KUxOtU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1KUxOtU.jpg&h=062292ee&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n以下大批警員表示會保護病人、醫護，市民就更加唔洗講啦！<br />\n有病可以搵警察陪同下去醫院求醫。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/75iCe8U.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F75iCe8U.jpg&h=c4437dbb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hDaw32d.jpg\" da